{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0001","text":"我對着青空許願 找一個寬廣的平原","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["願望","自由","愛情"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["青空","許願","平原","幸福"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,2,3,3,9,2,9,3,4,3,9,3,0,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","deoi3","zoek6","cing1","hung1","heoi2","jyun6","zaau2","jat1","go3","fun1","gwong2","dik1","ping4","jyun4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"對","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"青空","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"許願","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"寬廣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"平原","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以「我對着青空許願」開頭，表達對美好未來的期盼，並尋求一個寬廣的空間來實現。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002","text":"不需要磚 不須要穿 跟你 幸福愛戀","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","簡單","承諾"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["磚","穿","幸福","愛戀"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,4,3,3,3,4,3,3,5,2,3,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","seoi1","jiu3","zyun1","bat1","seoi1","jiu3","cyun1","gan1","nei5","hang6","fuk1","oi3","lyun2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"需要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"磚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"須要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"穿","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"幸福","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"愛戀","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以否定句「不需要」開頭，強調對物質的淡泊，只追求與愛人簡單的幸福。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003","text":"赤腳踏過青草地 烈日憑什麼好奇","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["自由","自然","好奇"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["赤腳","青草地","烈日","好奇"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,4,2,4,3,9,2,2,2,0,2,3,9,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cek3","goek3","daap6","gwo3","cing1","cou2","dei6","lit6","jat6","pang4","sam6","mo1","hou2","kei4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"赤","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"腳踏","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"青草地","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"烈日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"憑","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"好奇","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪赤腳走在青草地的畫面，並以擬人手法，將「烈日」比喻為一個有好奇心的人。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004","text":"風箏要飛雙相戀至死 天公都造美","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","承諾","命運"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["風箏","飛","相戀","天公","造美"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,4,3,3,9,4,9,3,3,3,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fung1","zang1","jiu3","fei1","soeng1","lyun2","zi3","sei2","tin1","gung1","dou1","zou6","mei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"風箏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"要","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"飛雙","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"相戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"至死","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天公","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"造美","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「風箏」比喻愛情的自由飛翔，並期望愛情能長久至死不渝，連上天也成全。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005","text":"含着笑 我宣佈 共你高貴地擁抱","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","尊嚴","承諾"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["笑","宣佈","高貴","擁抱"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,5,3,4,2,5,3,4,2,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ham4","zoek6","siu3","ngo5","syun1","bou3","gung6","nei5","gou1","gwai3","dei6","jung2","pou5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"含着","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"笑","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"宣佈","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"共","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"高貴","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"擁抱","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「含着笑」表達喜悅，並正式宣佈與愛人高貴地擁抱，展現對愛情的肯定。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006","text":"除下最漂亮錦袍 至少比蚯蚓驕傲","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","尊嚴","對比"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["錦袍","蚯蚓","驕傲"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,2,9,0,4,9,3,5,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ceoi4","haa6","zeoi3","piu1","loeng6","gam2","pou4","zi3","bei2","jau1","jan5","giu1","ngou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"除下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"最","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"漂亮","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"錦袍","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"至少","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"比","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"蚯蚓","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"驕傲","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「除下最漂亮錦袍」象徵放下外在的虛榮，並以「蚯蚓」作對比，強調即使平凡也因愛而感到驕傲。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007","text":"由我宣佈 共你於赤道起舞","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","自由","熱情"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["宣佈","赤道","起舞"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,3,4,2,5,3,4,2,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jau4","ngo5","syun1","bou3","gung6","nei5","jyu1","cek3","dou6","hei2","mou5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"由","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"宣佈","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"共","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"於","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"赤道","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"起舞","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"再次「宣佈」，這次是與愛人一同在「赤道」這個極端之地起舞，象徵熱情不受限制。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008","text":"誰若有十字架 請找愛去比武的 去殉道","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","犧牲","奉獻"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["十字架","愛","比武","殉道"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,2,2,9,9,9,4,4,9,5,3,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","joek6","jau5","sap6","zi6","gaa2","cing2","zaau2","oi3","heoi3","bei2","mou5","dik1","heoi3","seon1","dou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"若","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"十字架","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"請","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"比武","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"殉道","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「十字架」象徵犧牲，鼓勵人們為了愛去「比武」甚至「殉道」，表達對愛情的極致追求。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0009","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0009","text":"愛裏找不到恐懼 只恐怕找不到愛侶","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","恐懼","孤獨"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["愛","恐懼","愛侶"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,9,3,4,9,2,9,9,4,9,3,4,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","leoi5","zaau2","bat1","dou3","hung2","geoi6","zi2","hung2","paa3","zaau2","bat1","dou3","oi3","leoi5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛裏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"恐懼","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"恐怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛侶","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"表達在愛中沒有恐懼，但最大的恐懼是「找不到愛侶」，流露出對孤獨的擔憂。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0010","text":"相戀有福 幸運無罪 應該高呼萬歲","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","幸福","慶祝"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["相戀","有福","幸運","萬歲"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,5,3,2,2,0,2,3,3,3,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["lyun2","jau5","fuk1","hang6","wan6","mou4","zeoi6","goi1","gou1","fu1","maan6","seoi3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"相戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有福","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"幸運","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"無罪","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"應該","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"高呼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"萬歲","pos":"INTJ"}],"syntax_notes":"肯定相戀是「有福」和「幸運」的，並應「高呼萬歲」，表達對愛情的極大喜悅和讚頌。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0011","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0011","text":"我很好 就算因快樂嘔吐","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","極致","喜悅"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["快樂","嘔吐"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,9,2,4,3,4,2,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","han2","hou2","zau6","syun3","jan1","faai3","lok6","au2","tou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"很","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"好","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"就算","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"因","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"快樂","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"嘔吐","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以誇張的「快樂到嘔吐」來形容極致的喜悅，即使身體有不適反應，也甘之如飴。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0012","text":"誰若有十字架 請找缺少愛的 去哀悼","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","缺失","悲傷"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["十字架","缺少","愛","哀悼"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,2,2,9,9,9,4,4,3,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","joek6","jau5","sap6","zi6","gaa2","cing2","zaau2","kyut3","oi3","dik1","heoi3","oi1","dou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"若","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"十字架","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"請","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"找","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"缺少","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"哀悼","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"與第8行呼應，但這次是針對「缺少愛」的人，呼籲他們去「哀悼」，表達對缺乏愛的悲傷。"},"source":{"title":"光天化日","artists":["Wong"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3536","prev_line_id":"lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0011","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
